<s> To convey information to a screen reader without affecting a "normal" sighted browser, use alt text in a small transparent (or page background-colored) image.  </s>
<s> Such as: img src="spacer.gif"  </s>
<s> width="1" height="1" alt="The following sentance is of extreme importance."  </s>
<s> In a visual browser, the user will not see the alt text, even if the images are turned off since the alt text only shows within the size allocated for the image.  </s>
<s> They could see the alt text through the mouse-over effect, but only if they managed to put thier cursor over that one individual pixel.  </s>
